		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Permanent</strong> - 10 ft. Emanation (Self) - Magical</p><ul><li><p>You and allies can't be affected by the [charmed] condition.</p></li><li><p>If a creature who is already charmed comes within 10 ft. of you, this does not end the charmed condition, but does grant the creature advantage on saves to end the condition.</p></li><li><p>This ability does not function when you are &amp;reference[Petrified] or &amp;reference[Unconscious].</p></li></ul><p></p><p>At 18th level, the range of this aura increases to 30 feet (also listed below).</p>",
